name: RTCIceTransport.onselectedcandidatepairchange
description: The RTCIceTransport interface's onselectedcandidatepairchange event handler specifies a function to be called to handle the selectedcandidatepairchange event, which is fired when the ICE agent selects a new candidate pair to be used for the connection.
